                <div class="review-cons">
                    <h4>Cons</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Extremely expensive at $3,499</li>
                        <li>Heavy and difficult to move (over 200 lbs)</li>
                        <li>Touchscreen can be hard to see in direct sunlight</li>
                        <li>Overkill for occasional weekend grillers</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>

    <!-- Traeger Ironwood -->
    <article class="review-card" id="traeger-ironwood">
        <div class="review-header">
            <h3 class="review-title">Traeger Ironwood XL</h3>
            <div class="review-meta">
                <a href="https://amzn.to/3NmV8Xg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="review-price">$1,799</a>
                <span class="review-rating">Rating: 9.3/10</span>
